---
title: Loaded Mashed Potato Bar One recipe–endless ways to enjoy!
description: This family-style meal starts with a heaping bowl of fluffy mashed potatoes ready for topping with smoky bacon, charred corn, roasted green beans, white cheddar, crispy fried onions, sour cream, scallions, truffle butter, AND velvety homemade gravy. Stand back, behold your spread, and watch everyone build their ultimate bowl of comfort!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/668d42ae012d858ae3811d25-a534fab2.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/668ee7d449c4dd9a1d1cd884-en-US.pdf
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/loaded-mashed-potato-bar-668ee7d449c4dd9a1d1cd884
servings: 2
time required: 35 minutes
author: HelloFresh
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 1330 kcal
  fat: 94 g
  saturated fat: 44 g
  carbohydrates: 93 g
  sugar: 22 g
